#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.log.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.log"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log:1 of
msgid "Natural logarithm, element-wise."
msgstr "自然对数，逐元素计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log:3 of
msgid ""
"The natural logarithm `log` is the inverse of the exponential function, "
"so that `log(exp(x)) = x`. The natural logarithm is logarithm in base "
"`e`."
msgstr ""
"自然对数 `log` 是指数函数的反函数，因此 `log(exp(x)) = x`。自然对数是以 `"
"e` 为底的对数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log:7 of
msgid "Input value."
msgstr "输入值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log:9 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须与输入广播兼容。如果未提供或为 `"
"None`，则返回一个新分配的 tensor。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log:14 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log:19 of
msgid "**y** -- The natural logarithm of `x`, element-wise."
msgstr "**y** -- `x` 的自然对数，逐元素计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log:22 of
msgid ":py:obj:`log10`, :py:obj:`log2`, :py:obj:`log1p`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log:25 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log:26 of
msgid ""
"Logarithm is a multivalued function: for each `x` there is an infinite "
"number of `z` such that `exp(z) = x`. The convention is to return the `z`"
" whose imaginary part lies in `[-pi, pi]`."
msgstr ""
"对数是多值函数：对于每个 `x`，存在无限多个 `z` 使得 `exp(z) = x`。约定"
"返回虚部在 `[-pi, pi]` 范围内的 `z`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log:30 of
msgid ""
"For real-valued input data types, `log` always returns real output. For "
"each value that cannot be expressed as a real number or infinity, it "
"yields ``nan`` and sets the `invalid` floating point error flag."
msgstr ""
"对于实数输入数据类型，`log` 总是返回实数输出。对于不能表示为实数或无穷大"
"的值，它返回 ``nan`` 并设置 `invalid` 浮点错误标志。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log:34 of
msgid ""
"For complex-valued input, `log` is a complex analytical function that has"
" a branch cut `[-inf, 0]` and is continuous from above on it. `log` "
"handles the floating-point negative zero as an infinitesimal negative "
"number, conforming to the C99 standard."
msgstr ""
"对于复数输入，`log` 是一个复解析函数，其分支切割为 `[-inf, 0]`，并在其上"
"从上方连续。`log` 将浮点负零视为无穷小负数，符合 C99 标准。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log:40 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log:41 of
msgid ""
"M. Abramowitz and I.A. Stegun, \"Handbook of Mathematical Functions\", "
"10th printing, 1964, pp. 67. http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/"
msgstr ""
"M. Abramowitz 和 I.A. Stegun，《数学函数手册》，第10版，1964年，第67页。"
"http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log.log:43 of
msgid "Wikipedia, \"Logarithm\". http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Logarithm"
msgstr "维基百科，“对数”。http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Logarithm"

